channel.title: Linux Benchmark
channel.description:
If your Linux OS doesn't have HardInfo, please get it from here: http://hardinfo.berlios.de/HomePage Now check your Benchmarks and Post them here.
Im on a P4 3.06Ghz
CPU ZLib (higher is better) 16241.139
CPU Fibonacci (lower is better) 3.918
CPU MD5 (higher is better) 51.463
CPU SHA1 (higher is better) 60.903
CPU Blowfish (lower is better) 26.929
FPU Raytracing (lower is better) 32.083
